						Another day and another spirit shard to get, Peabodie had decided to take a trip and visit the land of giants. Well needless to say, that didn’t go too well for him! So we had to make a little expedition through the Giants and off to see the Fireguard!<br />
<br />
Here we are, putting some pain on a giant – and yes, that IS the angles you see of it! They are huge!<br />
